Error Fixes: 

/etc/shadowsocks-libev/manager.json: No such file or directory â€” 
Error occurs during the post-installation script of the omr-vps-admin package.
Below command This creates the missing directory and empty file, allowing the post-install script to finish cleanly.

mkdir -p /etc/shadowsocks-libev && touch /etc/shadowsocks-libev/manager.json && systemctl restart omr-admin

reboot
